 Canadian home, which really\u00a0adds up. You need to find an energy-efficient heating unit that will function\u00a0optimally for your home and help you save on your energy bill. 4 Seasons\u00a0provides installation and maintenance for\u00a0hot water heaters and boilers in Victoria. If you\u2019re looking to help the\u00a0environment and your wallet, <a href=\"https:\/\/4seasonsvictoria.com\/contact-us\/\">give us a\u00a0call today<\/a> to learn how an energy-efficient unit can benefit your home. To give you quality hot water and boiler units, we rely on some of the most reliable brands on the market.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;16px&#8221;]<div class=\"mkdf-accordion-holder mkdf-ac-default  mkdf-accordion mkdf-ac-boxed mkdf-white-skin   clearfix\">\n\t<h3 class=\"mkdf-accordion-title\" style=\"color: #cf1f3b\">\n    <span class=\"mkdf-tab-title\">Hot Water Heater Installation and Maintenance from 4 Seasons<\/span>\n    <span class=\"mkdf-accordion-mark\">\n\t\t<span class=\"mkdf_icon_plus icon_plus\"><\/span>\n\t\t<span class=\"mkdf_icon_minus icon_minus-06\"><\/span>\n\t<\/span>\n<\/h3>\n<div class=\"mkdf-accordion-content\">\n\t<div class=\"mkdf-accordion-content-inner\">\n\t\t[vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p class=\"bodytext\">With over 20 years of experience in the industry, we pride ourselves on our outstanding customer service, which means we won\u2019t just sell you a great hot water heater. We\u2019ll have our professional team install it, educate you on everything you need to know to properly maintain your unit, and we can also provide the applicable maintenance services to keep it running smoothly for years to come. For more information, <a href=\"https:\/\/4seasonsvictoria.com\/contact-us\/\">feel free to\u00a0contact us<\/a>. Take a look at some of the brands we carry:<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>\u2022\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bradfordwhite.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-track-event=\"click\" data-track-action=\"link_clicked\">Bradford White \u00ae<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2022\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bradfordwhite.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-track-event=\"click\" data-track-action=\"link_clicked\">JJ John Wood\u00ae<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2022\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.rheem.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-track-event=\"click\" data-track-action=\"link_clicked\">Rheem\u00ae<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2022\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.rinnai.us\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-track-event=\"click\" data-track-action=\"link_clicked\">Rinnai\u00ae<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2022\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.weil-mclain.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-track-event=\"click\" data-track-action=\"link_clicked\">Weil-McLain\u00ae<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2022\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.argoboiler.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-track-event=\"click\" data-track-action=\"link_clicked\">Argo<\/a>[\/vc_column_text]\t<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>[vc_empty_space height=&#8221;50px&#8221;][vc_separator][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;50px&#8221; el_class=&#8221;disapearing-space&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"subtitle\"><span class=\"text-mobile\" style=\"color: #e86026;\">Residential Hot Water Heaters, By the\u00a0Numbers<\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"bodytext\">While the initial cost of a hot water\u00a0heater is not something to scoff at, it\u2019s important to understand the over-time\u00a0operating costs of your unit. For example, let\u2019s say you use 225 litres of hot\u00a0water a day (Canadian average for family of 3*) over a 10-year period, and\u00a0electricity costs 10\u00a2 per kilowatt-hour. After 10 years, you will have spent\u00a0roughly $7,000 on energy costs from your hot water heater. If you\u2019re currently\u00a0using an older, less energy-efficient model, the cost could be even higher.\u00a0Rely on us to help you choose the right hot water heater for your home.<\/p>\n<p class=\"bodytext\">Information regarding energy\/water\u00a0consumption comes from\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.nrcan.gc.ca\/energy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-track-event=\"click\" data-track-action=\"link_clicked\">Natural\u00a0Resources Canada*<\/a><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"subtitle\"><span class=\"text-mobile\" style=\"color: #e86026;\">Water Heaters &amp; Maintenance by 4 Seasons\u00a0<\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"bodytext\">You can rely on the certified technicians at 4 Seasons for reliable water heater repairs and maintenance. Some of the services that we provide include but are not limited to:<\/p>\n<h5 style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"color: #1c9a69;\">Hot Water Heater:<\/span><\/h5>\n<p class=\"bodytext\" style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">\u2022\u00a0 Check operation of safety limit controls<\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">\u2022\u00a0 Check expansion tank (if applicable)<\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">\u2022\u00a0 Check water pressure, temperature relief valve and operation of thermostat<\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">\u2022\u00a0 Check pressure switches and vent blower (if applicable)<\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">\u2022\u00a0 Inspect burners and clean if required<\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">\u2022\u00a0 Examine vent connector and inspect venting system<\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">\u2022\u00a0 Check flame rectification<\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">\u2022\u00a0 Check gas piping and adjust manifold gas pressure<\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">\u2022\u00a0 Clean equipment interior\/exterior<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;100px&#8221; el_class=&#8221;mobile-space&#8221;][vc_separator][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;100px&#8221; el_class=&#8221;mobile-space&#8221;]<div class=\"mkdf-elements-holder   mkdf-two-columns  mkdf-responsive-mode-680 \" ><div class=\"mkdf-eh-item